:name:
Rigor

:coretxt:
Vampire posses mystical inhuman endurance. 
Can be used to remove incoming vigor damage but only up to three.

:cost:
1 Vigor per activation

:req:
Has seen the sun after transformation.

:1:
Skin like a crocodiles. Decrease incoming damage by one

:2:
Skin strong as bronze. Decrease incoming damage by two

:3:
Skin strong as steel. Decrease incoming damage by three. Survive in sunlight without any problem ten times to the normal.

:tags:
Vampiric
VampiricStrength
